      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MAHOME GIRL (1) had been racing in honest fashion recording two placings in a row before finishing fifth (20.25) at Gunnedah latest. Better than the latest effort and deserves another chance. TOTAL TEMPTATION (7) scored two back then drifted back and missed the frame latest finishing a 7 length 5th at Maitland (23.08). Good beginner but will need a little luck early crossing from an outside draw. Expected to feature in the finish. KARINYA TOM TOM (2) is an honest type who is lining up for his first start here. Raced on speed and lifted strongly to score a 2.5 lengths win over 340m at Gunnedah (20.01). Safe beginner who has drawn to advantage. Leading player again. RED ROCK LOTUS (8) placed last time out so worth considering.",
